HEADWORD: Chokecherry
<hw>Choke"cher`ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The astringent fruit of a species of wild cherry (<spn>Prunus
Virginiana</spn>); also, the bush or tree which bears such
fruit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

